<br>
It is those who answer well I got drunk one weekend and... that tell me they aren't really as thoughtful as I would like... unless that incident was in the past (long past) &amp; they know how foolish such a life decision was without fully thinking it through.<br>
<br>
I'm not sure I am coherent or just rambling... but take it all with a grain of salt.  What I want to say is people should be judged for themselves, not clothes, not wieght, not hair, not tats, not piercings, but for what is inside.<br>
<br>
-Caillou's player<br>
